&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:%20oldtimefamilybaseball@gmail.com" target="_blank"&gt;Shoot me an email&lt;/a&gt; or drop one in the comments, if you’d be so kind. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

Leave your tips in the comments or reblog with them.

